OL,3,C'Menace To Society' convicted over
OL,4,C#3.50 drug debt shooting
OL,6,FA music producer known as 'Menace to
OL,7,FSociety' has been convicted after
OL,8,Frepeatedly shooting through a window
OL,9,Fin retaliation over a #3.50 drug debt.
OL,11,FPolice said it was "sheer good
OL,12,Ffortune" the victim was not more
OL,13,Fseriously injured or killed after
OL,14,Fsuffering only superficial wounds from
OL,15,Fflying glass.
OL,17,FMarcus Adepoju, 31, was convicted of a
OL,18,Fstring of firearms and drug offences
OL,19,Fand tracked down by police scouring
OL,20,Fhours of CCTV footage.
