OL,3,C'Menace To Society' convicted over
OL,4,C#3.50 drug debt shooting
OL,6,F"Adepoju is an extremely dangerous
OL,7,Findividual who had no qualms about
OL,8,Fshooting a man through a window on a
OL,9,Fbusy residential street," said Det
OL,10,FConstable John Nightingale.J"Adepoju
OL,11,Fproduced music under the stage name
OL,12,F'Menace To Society' ` sadly his
OL,13,Factions reinforced this moniker and he
OL,14,Fwill now pay the price for his crimes.
OL,15,F"Keeping Londoners safe is our top
OL,16,Fpriority and reducing gun crime is a
OL,17,Fkey part of this. As this case shows,
OL,18,Fwe know gun crime is closely linked to
OL,19,Fdrugs and we will continue to use all
OL,20,Fof our resources to take both off the
OL,21,Fstreets of our capital."
