OL,3,C'Menace To Society' convicted over
OL,4,C#3.50 drug debt shooting
OL,6,FIn April 2023, officers were called to
OL,7,Fa house on Nelgarde Road in Catford
OL,8,Fwhere a man reported he had been shot
OL,9,Fat through a window by a masked man.
OL,10,FThe three shots had narrowly missed
OL,11,Fhim but caused superficial wounds from
OL,12,Fglass shards, as well as extensive
OL,13,Fdamage to the property.
