OL,3,C'Menace To Society' convicted over
OL,4,C#3.50 drug debt shooting
OL,6,FCCTV showed the suspect walking to the
OL,7,Fscene from a house in Hither Green and
OL,8,Freturning there soon afterwards.
OL,9,FOfficers focused their attention on
OL,10,Fthose coming in and out of the
OL,11,Fproperty and shortly afterwards they
OL,12,Fsaw a man ` later identified as Marcus
OL,13,FAdepoju ` travelling from the house to
OL,14,Fa storage facility in nearby Forest
OL,15,FHill.JA search of the unit recovered
OL,16,Ftwo firearms alongside ammunition,
OL,17,Fdrugs, cash and knives. Another
OL,18,Fstorage facility they linked to
OL,19,FAdepoju was found to contain more
OL,20,Fammunition, cash and drugs.
